Class BriteTopologyGenerator

  • java.lang.Object
    • grph.algo.topology.RandomizedTopologyTransform

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    TopologyGenerator

    public class BriteTopologyGenerator
extends RandomizedTopologyTransform
    Provides a bridge to the BRITE topology generator (http://www.cs.bu.edu/brite/).
